author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Kimberly-Clark Corp - Kim Underhill, President Of Kimberly-Clark Professional, Named Group President Kimberly-Clark North America
text:
May 11 (Reuters) - Kimberly-Clark Corp:
* KIMBERLY-CLARK CORP - KIM UNDERHILL, PRESIDENT OF KIMBERLY-CLARK PROFESSIONAL, HAS BEEN NAMED GROUP PRESIDENT KIMBERLY-CLARK NORTH AMERICA
* KIMBERLY-CLARK CORP - UNDERHILL IS SUCCEEDING LARRY ALLGAIER Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
